Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Dialogue,Credits,0,0,0,,Subtitle-source: Detective Conan - 251 [AZFS][39A9BBAD].avi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:06.02,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:06.02,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Matsuhashi Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reasons and hints are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With these, the truth unravels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case takes place at the OK Corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The battle between the crime and deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.74,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Something's just not right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.74,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Something's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:21.91,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,nani o motometeru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:21.91,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,What is it we're seeking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:26.63,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,uso ni narete yuku kyou mo fake your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:26.63,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,We're used to lying nowadays, as you fake your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.67,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,The start of century
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.67,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The start of century.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.18,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tashika na mono nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.18,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Nothing can be considered certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.27,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hitori ja nakenai yowasa hate myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.27,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can't cry over my weaknesses, I can only hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:51.03,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,shinjiteru itami hikikae ni kono mune umetsukushite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:51.03,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Believing in this pain, my chest endures through the exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.83,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima utsutte iru futari ga eranda michi kuru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.83,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The future that the two of us can be together is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.45,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.45,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.83,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hateshinai yami no mukou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.83,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,On the other side of this persistent darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.17,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,dare mo shiru koto no nai ashita ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.17,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,There's a tomorrow that has no time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.18,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,oh yeah. You're going nowhere, It's only destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.18,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. You're going nowhere, It's only destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.47,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ari no mama ni susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.47,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Looking for that final resolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.81,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima kanjite iru you're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.81,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can feel you now, you're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,you're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,You're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, mother nature is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Dad, why did you take us out for a drive all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't we pass by here awhile ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are here, and we need to get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look at where the destination is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Dad, make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OKusu Corral?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:44.26,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Tragedy at the OK Corral
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:48.23,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,OKUSU Ranch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saved me. I was able to arrive\Nhere on time because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hirohito Ninomiya (28)\NPart-Time Ranch Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been awhile since we've had customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this place is a horse ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we were forced to come and share his horse obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted you guys to fully enjoy the outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.43,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Mochizuki Kanenari (46)\NReal Estate Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No need to tell me. I was about to\Nleave anyway. I'm a busy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait until I sell this ranch, then you\Nwill realize that you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you guys had to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the OK Corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:45.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Okusu Tomoyuki (50)\NRanch Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner. My name is Okusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK Corral?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK Corral is the abbreviation for OKUSU Corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although this place isn't really "OK."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. Do you want some chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I will be your tour guide. My name\Nis Takeuchi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.74,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Takeuchi Sanae (21)\NPart-Time Ranch Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are in the middle of the racing season right\Nnow, so not all of the horses are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize any of these horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this horse Madam Leap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is the thoroughbred of this corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She made me a lot of money a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why doesn't she look so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was trying to breed but failed,\Nand now she can't breed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, how unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old barn is for horse breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's where foals are brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one uses it now, but if you want, you can go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are those customers, Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks for coming. It's Madam Leap's turn today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He helped me look after the corral when I was a rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Sugiyama Moto (37)\NFarrier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Sugiyama Moto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he's a farrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Farrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A farrier is a person who shoes horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.17,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Farrier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horses that live on farms get a lot of exercise, so horseshoes\Nare put on to protect the hooves from damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this prevents the hooves from being trimmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the horseshoes have to be taken off periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After trimming the hooves, the horseshoes\Nare put back on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are very knowledgeable about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Takeuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looks surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just something I've heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, they heat up the new horseshoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and reshape it to the right size of the horse's hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sizes of the hooves are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even for one horse, the size of each hoof\Nis different from the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it? Isn't it good that we came?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam Leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Madam Leap is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam Leap is running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Steady, steady, steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is her first time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is possible that he was kicked by Madam\NLeap, causing his head to bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, call the police immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take Madam Leap to another trough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A piece of chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The right rear hoof looks weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The horseshoe wasn't nailed on properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shapes of the horseshoe and the hoof don't match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let her drink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there still some tea in the thermos?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tea is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine for a human to drink, but it's a stimulant for horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tea is a stimulant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, this wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was kicked by the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there's an imprint of a horseshoe on his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, it's best to check if the horseshoe\Nmatches the shape of the imprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I am a private detective, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this is an accident, so you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of curiosity, what's going to happen to Madam Leap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's best to just get rid of this violent horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! It is all Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fault. He deserved to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you hate Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did he deserve to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, on my way back from town...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama was meeting with Mochizuki,\Nwho wants to buy the OK Corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okusu is trying to get the horse breeding again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he fails again this time, he will go bankrupt for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we will do again what we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will leave it to you, Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of money, Sugiyama betrayed Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama showed up before I could\Nsay anything to Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Based off Manga\NNone (Anime Original)
Comment: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Original Air Date\NSeptember 3rd, 2001
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, in order to make this ranch go bankrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mochizuki told Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to\Ninterrupt the breeding process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. There's a huge amount\Nof money involved in breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hence, we lose money if there are no foals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam Leap got involved in this human struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, would the horse try to get revenge because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she did, then she's no different than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that horse looks sad, her eyes are still clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no place for kids to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, your pants are wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got splashed when I was cleaning the stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry that you got wet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This incident will probably be treated as an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to take the horseshoe with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't the police supposed to gather all the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will go get the horseshoe if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did everything myself back then anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No money to hire a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't have any before, and certainly don't have any now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please put it in this plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This horseshoe has blood on the back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, and a huge amount of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. It's all clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know the culprit, and the method used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how strong the horse may be, it's hard\Nfor the blood to get on the back of the horseshoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then there is only one answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood was there from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Madam Leap's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The nails are not properly nailed on to the horseshoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They even penetrated through some blood vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel, this is all Sugiyama's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why the horse was out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing, except that I know how\NSugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, show everyone what you found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this. I picked it up off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was beside the trough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how is this related to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To horses, tea is like a stimulant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same goes for chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocolate has theobromine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone gave chocolate to Madam Leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where is the chocolate that you\Nwere going to give to Conan earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh that... It's still in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I remember that you actually put it in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} be the one who used the chocolate\Nand made Madam Leap go out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, maybe Madam Leap didn't eat the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can be checked if the horse's urine is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, if we check for fingerprints on the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will be able to know whose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave Madam Leap the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you hated Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you shouldn't\Nhave used Madam Leap to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was not killed by Madam Leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:17:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is the person who put the unfitted horseshoe\Nonto Madam Leap's rear right hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it is not Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who put the horseshoe on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the job was not done properly, even if it was a\None-time error, he could no longer be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would become jobless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it is Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood\Non the back of the horseshoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit probably used a newly made horseshoe\Nto hit the back of Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he didn't know what to do with it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, panicking, he quickly nailed it on to Madam Leap's hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you were in a rush, you wouldn't put\Nthe horseshoe on so carelessly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There might have been some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of making it look like an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would be wiser to take the weapon\Nand run away before anyone noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this murder was planned, then it wouldn't\Nhave been done so sloppily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is right, Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} shouldn't be\Nbad at putting horseshoes on horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since he wanted to take off the\Nhorseshoe as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it seemed to me like he already knew\Nthat the horseshoe was put on badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on that observation, I figured out\Nhe already knew who the culprit was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to protect the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he gave Madam Leap chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he went back to the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and waited for Madam Leap to start acting erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did this to cause us to focus our attention on the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying so hard to protect the person.\NHe even gave chocolate to the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was with us the whole\Ntime, so she can't be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, there is only one\Nperson left. Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your pants are wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they are tested with luminol, they should show blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From putting the bloody horseshoe on the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, because that horseshoe did not fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was troublesome to put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it has mud on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be out of the ordinary since this is a ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, if the victim's blood is on it instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it will be obvious that something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I couldn't forgive Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:20:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was curious, so I went straight to Sugiyama\Nand asked about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he was going to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make it look like a simple accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then took out a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I made it look like Madam Leap's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting a horse in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's a dirty deed, I know that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be saying sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually noticed that there was something\Nnot right about Sugiyama before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are very noble. I was afraid that if I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,things would get even worse, so I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had known that this would happen,\NI would've told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninomiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Okusu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to pay for what you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you try to hide it,\Nit will not solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship and sympathy can never supersede the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Aoi Aoi Kono Hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Uehara Azumi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:54.37,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}shigekiteki na sekai o matte ita kedo kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:54.37,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I'm waiting for a world that's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:22:01.00,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}me no mae ni aru subete ga taisetsu na mono nanda ne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:22:01.00,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}But maybe everything before me is precious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:13.56,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ushinau koto kowagaru nante... watashitachi mada nani mo iretenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:13.56,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}To be afraid of losing something... we haven't got anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.06,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}oh, yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.90,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}aoi aoi kono hoshi ni kagirinai mirai kasane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.90,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}In this blue, blue world, limitless possible futures expand out before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.11,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}can make me free kono mama kodou kanjite itai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.11,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Can make me free, I don't want my heart to stop racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.61,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}oh, yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.37,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}kono kimochi maiagare sore to umi yaki tsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.37,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}This feeling starts to dance within me, burning the sky and boiling the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:43.17,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}tsuyoi chikara de kimi ni dakare tobidashitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:43.17,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I want you to embrace me tightly in your arms, and take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.30,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}oh, yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:52.14,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}kono kimochi maiagare sore to umi yaki tsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:52.14,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}This feeling starts to dance within me, burning the sky and boiling the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:23:01.77,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}tsuyoi chikara de kimi ni dakare tobidashitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:23:01.77,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I want you to embrace me tightly in your arms, and take off.
